name: SafeCycle
description: Brother's latest technology, SafeCycle, helps you to be safer on the roads. Using state-of-the-art GPS technology and proprietary software, this device will automatically call for assistance whenever it detects that you have an accident. Its easy to use UI allows you to have full customisation - including what colours the device will flash when it detects a problem.
